thread.title: Israelis kill dozens of protesters as US moves embassy

title: Israelis kill dozens of protesters as US moves embassy
text:
Israelis kill 41 protesters as US moves embassy 6:49pm IST - 01:12
Israeli gunfire killed dozens and wounded at least 500 other protesters along the Gaza border on Monday, health officials said, as demonstrators streamed to the frontier on the day the United States prepared to open its embassy in Jerusalem.
Israeli gunfire killed 28 Palestinians and wounded at least 500 other protesters along the Gaza border on Monday, health officials said, as demonstrators streamed to the frontier on the day the United States prepared to open its embassy in Jerusalem. //reut.rs/2GdOZnK
